==English==

===Etymology===
1814, from {{compound|hand|book|lang=en}}, or perhaps a reintroduction of {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|handbōc}} "handbook", or a loan-translation of {{etyl|de|-}} {{m|de|Handbuch}}
"handbook". Compare {{etyl|nl|-}} {{m|nl|handboek}}, {{etyl|da|-}} {{m|da|håndbog}}, {{etyl|sv|-}} {{m|sv|handbok}}.

